dbu ma'i lam 'di skad bzang 'ga' yis rnyed
'jam pa'i dbyangs dang 'phags mchog klu sgrub dang
mnyam med chos kyi rgyal po tsong kha pa
dbyer med zhabs kyi padmor phyag byas nas
mtha' bral lta ba'i nyams len brjod par bya
'di na dang po'i las can 'ga' zhig la
'di tsam gyis kyang cung zad phan 'gyur zhes
lhag bsam dkar bas yi ger bkod pa'i mthus
'gro kun mtha' bral lta dang mi 'bral shog
gang gi zhabs sen spyi bor reg pas kyang
srid pa'i 'jigs 'phrog don gnyis 'dod dgu'i dpal
skad cig nyid la lag rtser stsol mdzad pa
yab rje bla ma'i zhabs la phyag 'tshal lo
yin lugs mthar thug rtogs pa lta ba ste
bying rgod bral ba'i nyams myong sgom pa yin
thabs shes zung du 'brel ba spyod pa ste
sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa 'bras bur 'dod
rkyen gyis ma bcos ngo bo 'gyur ba med
rang bzhin rnam dag gshis la bzang ngan bral
kun khyab kun gyi rang bzhin gdod ma'i gshis
spros pa'i mtha' bral rtogs pa lta ba yin
rnam rtog pir gyis ri mo bris tsam las
yul gyi steng nas grub pa ma mchis kyang
ming tsam nyid la 'khor 'das bya byed kun
'thad par shes pa gnas lugs mthong ba lags
ji lta ba dang ji snyed don rnams la
so sor dpyod dang ri dbang bzhin du 'jog
'dod dgur dbang sgyur bying rgod dang bral bas
ting 'dzin sgo brgya 'byed de sgom par 'dod
g.yo med shin tu brtan pa'i zhi gnas dang
yin lugs so sor dpyod pa'i lhag mthong gnyis
zung du 'brel bas sgrib gnyis sa bon kun
spong bar 'dod de sgom chen pa zhes bya
'khor ba mya ngan 'das pa thams cad kyi
gdod ma'i gshis la dbye ba ma mchis kyang
tha snyad las 'bras bslu ba med shes nas
phyin drug nyams su len pa spyod pa yin
gzhi yi lta ba snang stong zung 'jug ste
lam gyi nyams len tshogs gnyis zung du 'brel
'bras bu sku gnyis zung 'jug lhun gyis grub
rgyal ba dgyes pa'i lta sgom spyod 'bras lags
'jam dbyangs klu sgrub zhabs dang tsong kha pa
dbyer med zhabs kyi padmor snying nas 'dud
don gnyer skal bzang rgyud la mtha' bral gyi
lta ba rnam dag myur du skyed du
las 'bras kyi blang dor la mkhas par bya'o
sras bcas rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs rje dang
mgon po 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyi byin rlabs dang
rtsa brgyud bla ma'i bka' drin kho na las
mtha' bral lta ba myur du rtogs par shog
ji ltar mdang sum gnyid kyis log pa na
dgra dang gnyen sogs snang ba gang shar yang
sad tshe grub pa rdul tsam ma mchis pa
chos rnams thams cad de bzhin rtogs par shog
sgyu ma mkhan gyis rta dang glang po sogs
ji snyed yod yod lta bur sprul na yang
don la grub pa cung zad ma mchis pa
chos kun rtag tu de bzhin 'char bar shog
de ltar rtog pas btags tsam 'ba' zhig las
yul gyi steng nas grub pa skad cig kyang
med par rtogs pa lta ba'i nyams len gyis
srid pa'i rtsa ba drungs nas 'byin par shog
chos kun rang bzhin rnam par dag pa dang
tha snyad rten 'brel bslu ba ma mchis pa'i
bden pa de yis gnas lugs zab mo'i don
ji bzhin mngon du 'gyur ba'i bkra shis shog
rten dang brten pa'i 'khor lo'i chu klung 'bum
spro dang sdu mdzad dpal ldan bsnyems ma'i bdag
byang chub sems kyi rdo rje des skyongs shig
blo bzang dri med mkhyen pa'i me long la
shes bya'i gzugs kun gsal ba grags pa'i dpal
rna ba'i bdud rtsir 'thung tshe dad pa yi
spu long g.yos so brtse ba'i lcags kyus zungs
dus mtha' 'dir yang rje btsun 'jam pa'i dbyangs
'gro la legs bshad dga' ston stsol ba'i slad
blo gros mkha' ltar yangs pa'i bshes gnyen gyi
rnam par shar ba bdag gi mgon du gyur
gzhan dang mi mnyam rnam dpyod byed pa yis
bsgrubs pa'i legs bshad phra mo'i cha shas tsam
yi ge'i gzugs gyis shog bu'i me long la
gsal bar 'phos pa'i ri mo e ma mtshar
blo gros 'dab ma'i rlung shugs mi dman zhing
legs bshad mgrin pa'i rdza rnga rdung bzhin du
blo bzang dgongs don yid bzhin mtsho chen por
'dod dgur 'jug pa'i mthu ldan skal ba bzang
slar yang tshe rabs kun tu dam pa'i mgon
yab sras bla ma'i lugs dang mi 'bral zhing
log pa'i lam dang de yi srol 'dzin pa
sdig pa'i bshes dang phrad par ma gyur cig
'di ni mtho ris dpal mo'i nyams len du
go sla'i ngag gi bsdus nas bshad pa ste
sku gnyis lag rjes 'jog byed theg mchog gi
snying po mchog 'di nyams su len 'tshal lo
'phags pas rjes bzung dge slong dpal mo dang
grub chen snyan nas brgyud pa'i dmar khrid ces
bod 'dir grags pa'i lam gyi srol gnyis las
phyi ma'i nyams len mdor bsdus 'di ltar ro
bla ma'i rnal 'byor tshul bzhin bsgoms pa las
zab mo'i lam bzang skye ba'i rgyud smin cing
stobs bzhi tshang ba'i rdor sems sgom bzlas kyis
'gal rkyen sdig ltung thog ma nyid du sbyang
de nas swa b+hA wa yi sngags kyi don
dran pas yul snang thams cad stong par sbyang
stong pa'i ngang las dri med pad zla'i steng
rang sems hrIH las pad dkar 'dab brgyad ni
yu ba hrIH yig gis mtshan de nyid las
'od 'phros don byas 'dus las rang nyid ni
gangs ri ltar dkar 'phags mchog spyan ras gzigs
rtsa ba'i phyag gnyis thugs kar thal sbyar zhing
'og mas shel phreng chu skyes dkar po bsnams
dar gyi na bza' rin chen rgyan phreng can
rdo rje'i skyil krung gis bzhugs gnas gsum du
'bru gsum gyis mtshan thugs ka'i hrIH yig las
'od 'phros rdo rje gsum gyi lha yi tshogs
'phags pa'i sku yi rnam par rang lus la
thim pas rang lus yi dam kun 'dus dang
spyi bor bla ma snang ba mtha' yas kyi
sku la rtsa brgyud bla ma ma lus pa
bstims pas bla ma kun 'dus nyid du bsam
de bzhin snying gar zla steng hrIH yig mthar
'khod pa'i yi ge drug pa'i sngags phreng la
yi dam kun gyi snying po nye snying dang
phreng sngags la sogs kun thim thams cad kyi
snying po 'dus pa'i bdag nyid can du bsam
snod kyi 'jig rten mtha' dag gzhal yas khang
bcud kyi 'gro kun 'phags mchog spyan ras gzigs
sgrar snang thams cad yi ge drug ma'i gdangs
rang sems stong nyid snying rje 'du 'bral med
de ltar kun 'dus gsum dang 'khyer so gsum
'bral med ngang nas yi ge drug ma'i sngags
tshul bzhin zlo ba mtshan bcas rnal 'byor ro
'di na snang zhing srid pa'i chos rnams kun
rmi lam snang ba sgyu ma mig 'khrul bzhin
snang yang ngo bos grub pa rdul tsam yang
med par sgom pa mtshan med rnal 'byor ro
de nas zas gos gnas mal thams cad kyang
'bru gsum brjod pas de dag rim pa bzhin
stong pa nyid dang bdud rtsi lha yi gos
gzhal yas khang dang de dag nam mkha'i khams
gang bar sems pa lha yi rnal 'byor dang
ldan pas sred zhen bral bas longs spyod pa
de ni thun mtshams nyid kyi rnal 'byor yin
nyal tshe rang nyid lhar bsam spyi bor ni
bla ma kun 'dus bcom ldan 'od dpag med
snying ga'i d+hU tIr yi dam kun 'dus hrIH
gnyid du 'gro tshe gnyis ka'ang thig le'i gzugs
snying gar kha sbyar de la sems gzung bas
gnyid kyi 'od gsal 'char tshe mgrin pa'i dbus
rmi lam sgyu ma'i rnam rol ci yang 'byung
gnyid chen sgom du bsgyur ba'i man ngag go
d+hU tI'i mar snang thig le sngo dmar dbus
rang sems thig le dkar po yungs 'bru tsam
'og gi rlung 'then hi ka drag brjod pas
skar mda' bzhin du snying dbus yi dam gyi
thugs kar thim tshe rang sems spyan ras gzigs
dbyer med de nyid slar yang d+hU tI nas
tshangs bug lam song kaSha yig haM yig bcas
steng gi mkha' la 'phar zhing spyi bor ni
bzhugs pa'i bla ma snang ba mtha' yas kyi
thugs ka'i 'od zer lcags kyus reg tsam las
rang sems yi dam dbyer med tshangs bug nas
rgyangs te thon nas bla ma'i thugs kar thim
bla ma rdzu 'phrul stobs kyis nam mkha' las
bde ba can du thogs med gshegs par bsam
de ni sdig can btsan thabs 'tshang rgya ba'i
zab lam 'pho ba'i rnal 'byor de nyid do
sprin gseb glog 'gyu'i tshul dang chu klung las
nya ldang bzhin du 'chi ba 'od gsal gyi
rlung sems nyid las bar do grub pa na
rang lus snod bcud lha yi gzhal yas dang
ngag ni sngags kyi dkyil 'khor rang gi sems
dkyil 'khor gsum dang 'bral med ngang nyid nas
dag pa'i zhing ngam lha mi'i skye gnas su
bsams bzhin chos la spyod pa'i lus kyi rten
'dzin pa gang de bar do'i nyams len no
de ltar zab mo'i lam gyi gnad rnams kun
tshang zhing gsal la shin tu go sla bar
dad brtson ldan pa rgyal mtshan dpal de la
dge 'dun rgya mtsho'i dpal gyis legs par gdams
dam chos sbrang rtsi 'byung ba'i gnas
chu skyes rnam par rgyas pa'i thang
theg pa chen po'i pho brang nas
zab mo'i dbyangs su bsgrags pa yin
! bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo
bdag 'dzin chod par byin gyis rlobs
mdun gyi nam mkhar pad sdong la
bla ma lab kyi sgron ma la
mkha' 'gro sde lnga brgyud pa yi
bla ma rnams dang dkon cog gsum
mkha' 'gro chos skyong tshogs bcas bsam
de nas bem rig phral byas shing
dbyings dang rig pa dbyer med dang
rang nyid khros ma nag mor bsgom

rigs drug kun la rab tu sbyin
'khor gsum dmigs pa med par bya
rtse gcig chos kyi sku ru bsngo
slar yang sngar bzhin bem rig phral
dbyings rig bsres nas rnal 'byor mas
phyag g.yas 'bar ba'i gri gug gis
rang gi phung po kha phye nas

mnar med dmyal ba yan chad kyi

sha zos khrag 'thungs rus pa mur
thams cad bdud rtsis tshim par bsam
gzhan yang 'dre gdon ma lus pa
pha mar bsams la byams brtse bsgom
bla ma bsams la mchod pa dbul
yi dam du bsams dngos grub zhu
chos skyong du bsams 'phrin las bcol
phyi nang gsang ba'i bslongs lhong tshad dang
